= The 7th Saga (SNES) - RAM Map =

This page documents the RAM memory layout for The 7th Saga.

==Overview==

The 7th Saga uses the standard SNES memory map with 128 KB of work RAM.

{| class="wikitable"
! Range !! Size !! Description
|-
| $7e0000-$7e1fff || 8 KB || Zero Page, Stack, and Low RAM
|-
| $7e2000-$7effff || 56 KB || Main Work RAM
|-
| $7f0000-$7fffff || 64 KB || Extended Work RAM (used for decompression buffers, map data, etc.)
|}

